Appendix:
List of basic arithmetic operators:
•	Addition (+)
•	Subtraction (-)
•	Multiplication (*)
•	Division (/)
•	Modulus (Remainder) (%)
•	Increment (++)
•	Decrement (--)
•	Exponentiation (**)
•	Unary negation (-)
•	Unary plus (+)
